          "date": "2017-03-22 01:11:18.000000000",
          "tz": -420
        },
        "subject": "LU-2435 osd-zfs: for test only",
        "message": "LU-2435 osd-zfs: for test only\n\nIf ZFS userobj_accounting feature exists, use it for osd-zfs object\naccounting; otherwise estimate object use by block space.\n\nDisable quota check in conf-sanity:32b if the underlying zfs version\nis below 0.7.0. For ZFS 0.7.0 and higher, upgrade the zpool image to\nenable dnode quota accounting. That ensures we also test the upgrade\nprocedure.\n\nTest-Parameters: fortestonly mdtfilesystemtype=zfs testlist=sanity-quota,sanity-quota,sanity-quota,conf-sanity,conf-sanity envdefinitions=SLOW=yes\nSigned-off-by: Jinshan Xiong <jinshan.xiong@intel.com>\nChange-Id: Ib4a441c7caeff3624214fad16f9f4110bdc2bd12\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
